    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80c4-ba48-c18da3da41c1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Understanding how students problem-solve is an esencial tool towards developing better tools to fully develop their learning process. The approach starts with survey collection and the answers are processed using NLP techniques. The discovery process revealed 18 distinct learning approaches. Simultaneously, the results also show that learners use tools that vary significantly from task to task. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80c4-ba48-c18da3da41c1",
        "parent": {
